<function>

access:   protected

name: _pathEncode

param: array, $spec

return: string

</function>

Converts an array of path elements into a string.

* Parameters:

 * array //$spec//: The path elements.

* Returns string: A URI path string.

Converts an array of path elements into a string.

Does not use [[php urlencode()]]; instead, only converts
characters found in Solar_Uri::$_encode_path.